410
00:28:35,600 --> 00:28:38,520
We did things our own way.

411
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:41,400
We were four friends.

412
00:28:41,760 --> 00:28:46,320
Jackie, Pauline, Céline...

413
00:28:46,560 --> 00:28:48,480
