473
00:32:10,040 --> 00:32:13,760
And I put more clothing
over my belly.

474
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:16,200
And I walked like this.

475
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:18,760
That way, she would get it.

476
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:24,160
And I said:

477
00:32:24,360 --> 00:32:28,120
