791
00:53:07,040 --> 00:53:09,560
Look how empty it was.

792
00:53:11,040 --> 00:53:13,680
You could stand up
and take photos.

793
00:53:14,000 --> 00:53:16,080
Rosine strikes a pose...

794
00:53:16,840 --> 00:53:19,000
You posed.

795
