Beg him to pardon me.

1191
01:20:01,760 --> 01:20:05,160
Don't leave me here like this, Mom.

1192
01:20:08,280 --> 01:20:11,440
Ask forgiveness for me,
do it for your child.

1193
01:20:11,800 --> 01:20:13,520
