memories of family.

1232
01:27:13,720 --> 01:27:16,160
How many times
have we laughed about our culture,

1233
01:27:16,280 --> 01:27:19,160
or this new culture
we were getting to know,

1234
01:27:19,480 --> 01:27:23,200
imagining that one day
all would go well for us here?

1235
